 ans:["I'm looking for a smart-casual blazer for both office and evenings. Versatility is key.","My style is minimalist — clean lines, neutral colours. I own a lot of black so I'm thinking navy.","Quality comes first. I'd rather spend more on something that lasts five years.","The medium fits perfectly in the shoulders but the sleeves are slightly long. Can you alter?","I'd always prefer a full cash refund if possible. I've had bad experiences with store credit.","That sounds useful — I find shopping stressful when I don't know what I need.","Fewer but better pieces — timeless over trendy. Things I can wear for ten years."],
