 qs:[["How can I help you today — first time with us?","Чем могу помочь — вы первый раз у нас?"],["Tell me about your financial needs and what you're looking for.","Расскажите о ваших финансовых потребностях."],["There was an unusual transaction — can you walk me through recent activity?","Была необычная транзакция — расскажите о недавних операциях?"],["You want to send money internationally — explain the purpose?","Вы хотите отправить деньги за рубеж — объясните цель?"],["Do you understand the fees and interest rates before you sign?","Вы понимаете комиссии и ставки перед подписанием?"],["Your credit score is affecting your options — can you explain your history?","Ваш кредитный рейтинг влияет на варианты — расскажите историю?"],["Tell me about your longer-term financial goals.","Расскажите о ваших долгосрочных финансовых целях?"]],
 ans:["I'd like to open a current account and explore savings options. I recently moved to the city.","I need a reliable account for salary, seamless online banking, eventually saving for property.","I was in Berlin last week and used my card there. Also bought expensive tech equipment online.","I send money to my parents in Russia monthly — around 500 dollars. What's the best method?","I understood the annual fee to be 1.5% and savings interest 2.3%. Are there other charges?","I had difficulties two years ago after redundancy. Fell behind on a card but it's fine now.","My goal is to buy property in 3–5 years and invest conservatively alongside that."],
