 ans:["My laptop keeps freezing about 20 minutes after startup. Started two days ago with no obvious trigger.","MacBook Pro 2021, macOS Ventura. Updated about a week ago — actually, around the same time this started.","Consistently every time — about 20 minutes in the screen goes unresponsive. Happening right now.","I installed a new video editing app last week. Hadn't connected that until you asked.","I'm reasonably comfortable — just talk me through it and I'll tell you what I see.","A same-day store appointment would be ideal — I rely on this laptop and can't be without it."],
